{
  "work_slug": "the-maltese-falcon-by-dashiell-hammett",
  "work_title": "Maltese Falcon, Original Serialized Version",
  "work_author": "Dashiell Hammett",
  "audio_file": "audio-16",
  "audio_url": "https://archive.org/download/maltesefalcon_2511_librivox/maltesefalcon_16_hammett.mp3",
  "chapter_title": "Chapter 16 - The Third Murder",
  "reader_name": "Mark Nelson",
  "page_num": 5,
  "page_total": 6,
  "page_start_sec": 988.02,
  "page_end_sec": 1228.32,
  "para_gap_threshold": 0.671,
  "segments": [
    {
      "start": 988.02,
      "end": 989.56,
      "text": "His fingers tore the wad apart,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 989.82,
      "end": 991.66,
      "text": "and then he had the foot-high"
    },
    {
      "start": 991.8,
      "end": 992.68,
      "text": "figure of a bird,"
    },
    {
      "start": 992.96,
      "end": 995.48,
      "text": "black as coal and shiny where its"
    },
    {
      "start": 995.48,
      "end": 997.7,
      "text": "polish was not dulled by wood-dust and"
    },
    {
      "start": 997.74,
      "end": 998.9,
      "text": "fragments of excelsior."
    },
    {
      "start": 1000.32,
      "end": 1001.04,
      "text": "Spade laughed.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1001.792,
      "end": 1003.38,
      "text": "He put a hand down on the bird,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1003.6,
      "end": 1004.82,
      "text": "a hand whose widespread"
    },
    {
      "start": 1005.06,
      "end": 1007.0,
      "text": "red fingers had ownership in their curving."
    },
    {
      "start": 1007.22,
      "end": 1009.68,
      "text": "He put his other arm around Effie Perrine"
    },
    {
      "start": 1009.86,
      "end": 1011.4,
      "text": "and crushed her body to his."
    },
    {
      "start": 1012.832,
      "end": 1013.9,
      "text": "\"'We've got the damn thing,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1013.94,
      "end": 1015.1,
      "text": "Angel,' he said."
    },
    {
      "start": 1015.54,
      "end": 1016.18,
      "text": "\"'Ouch!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1016.24,
      "end": 1017.28,
      "text": "You're hurting me!'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1017.67,
      "end": 1019.32,
      "text": "He took his arm away from her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1019.42,
      "end": 1021.28,
      "text": "picked the black bird up in both hands,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1021.44,
      "end": 1022.2,
      "text": "and shook it"
    },
    {
      "start": 1022.2,
      "end": 1024.04,
      "text": "to dislodge clinging excelsior."
    },
    {
      "start": 1025.06,
      "end": 1025.9,
      "text": "Then he stepped back,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1026.08,
      "end": 1027.34,
      "text": "holding it up in front of him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1027.48,
      "end": 1027.96,
      "text": "blowing"
    },
    {
      "start": 1028.06,
      "end": 1028.76,
      "text": "dust off it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1028.84,
      "end": 1030.18,
      "text": "regarding it triumphantly."
    },
    {
      "start": 1031.03,
      "end": 1033.92,
      "text": "Effie Perrine made a horrified face and screamed,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1034.24,
      "end": 1035.3,
      "text": "pointing at his feet."
    },
    {
      "start": 1036.68,
      "end": 1037.9,
      "text": "He looked down at his feet.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1038.16,
      "end": 1041.72,
      "text": "His last backward step had brought his left heel into contact"
    },
    {
      "start": 1041.84,
      "end": 1043.1,
      "text": "with the dead man's hand,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1043.56,
      "end": 1045.4,
      "text": "pinching a quarter-inch of flesh at"
    },
    {
      "start": 1045.4,
      "end": 1047.26,
      "text": "a side of the palm between heel and"
    },
    {
      "start": 1047.34,
      "end": 1047.54,
      "text": "floor."
    },
    {
      "start": 1048.768,
      "end": 1050.56,
      "text": "Spade jerked his foot away from the hand.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1051.68,
      "end": 1052.76,
      "text": "The telephone bell rang.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1053.76,
      "end": 1054.72,
      "text": "He nodded at the girl.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1055.48,
      "end": 1057.96,
      "text": "She turned to the desk and put the receiver to her ear.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1058.14,
      "end": 1058.78,
      "text": "She said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1058.94,
      "end": 1059.04,
      "text": "Hello?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1059.96,
      "end": 1060.82,
      "text": "Yes?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1061.14,
      "end": 1061.84,
      "text": "Who?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1062.1,
      "end": 1062.92,
      "text": "Oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1062.94,
      "end": 1065.2,
      "text": "yes!\" Her eyes became large."
    },
    {
      "start": 1065.94,
      "end": 1066.2,
      "text": "Yes!",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1066.44,
      "end": 1066.92,
      "text": "Yes!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1067.22,
      "end": 1068.24,
      "text": "Hold the line!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1068.56,
      "end": 1069.4,
      "text": "Her mouth"
    },
    {
      "start": 1069.4,
      "end": 1071.0,
      "text": "suddenly stretched wide and fearful."
    },
    {
      "start": 1071.2,
      "end": 1071.98,
      "text": "She cried,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1072.44,
      "end": 1072.9,
      "text": "Hello!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1073.14,
      "end": 1073.68,
      "text": "Hello!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1074.06,
      "end": 1074.64,
      "text": "Hello!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1075.02,
      "end": 1076.2,
      "text": "into the telephone."
    },
    {
      "start": 1077.16,
      "end": 1078.48,
      "text": "She rattled the hook and cried,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1078.6,
      "end": 1079.1,
      "text": "Hello!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1079.44,
      "end": 1079.86,
      "text": "twice."
    },
    {
      "start": 1080.9,
      "end": 1083.22,
      "text": "Then she sobbed and jumped around to face Spade,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1083.24,
      "end": 1084.74,
      "text": "who was close beside her now."
    },
    {
      "start": 1085.792,
      "end": 1087.32,
      "text": "It was Miss O'Shaughnessy,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1087.44,
      "end": 1088.68,
      "text": "she said wildly."
    },
    {
      "start": 1088.96,
      "end": 1089.88,
      "text": "She wants you."
    },
    {
      "start": 1090.02,
      "end": 1091.06,
      "text": "She's in danger."
    },
    {
      "start": 1091.39,
      "end": 1092.02,
      "text": "She's at the"
    },
    {
      "start": 1092.08,
      "end": 1092.56,
      "text": "Alexandria."
    },
    {
      "start": 1093.4,
      "end": 1094.69,
      "text": "Her voice was—oh,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1094.9,
      "end": 1095.52,
      "text": "it was awful,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1095.64,
      "end": 1095.86,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 1096.08,
      "end": 1098.36,
      "text": "And something happened to her before she could"
    },
    {
      "start": 1098.46,
      "end": 1098.76,
      "text": "finish."
    },
    {
      "start": 1098.94,
      "end": 1099.94,
      "text": "Go help her,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1100.02,
      "end": 1100.24,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 1101.536,
      "end": 1104.28,
      "text": "Spade put the falcon on the desk and scowled gloomily."
    },
    {
      "start": 1105.44,
      "end": 1107.12,
      "text": "I've got to take care of this fellow first,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1107.34,
      "end": 1107.94,
      "text": "he said,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1108.02,
      "end": 1109.84,
      "text": "pointing his thumb at the thin corpse on"
    },
    {
      "start": 1109.98,
      "end": 1110.26,
      "text": "the floor."
    },
    {
      "start": 1111.48,
      "end": 1113.12,
      "text": "She beat his chest with her fists,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1113.3,
      "end": 1113.72,
      "text": "crying,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1114.34,
      "end": 1114.5,
      "text": "No!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1114.86,
      "end": 1116.28,
      "text": "You've got to go to her!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1116.44,
      "end": 1117.42,
      "text": "Don't you see,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1117.5,
      "end": 1117.8,
      "text": "Sam?"
    },
    {
      "start": 1118.36,
      "end": 1119.32,
      "text": "He had the thing that"
    },
    {
      "start": 1119.32,
      "end": 1119.82,
      "text": "was hers,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1120.08,
      "end": 1121.64,
      "text": "and he came to you with it!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1122.336,
      "end": 1122.94,
      "text": "Don't you see?",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1123.28,
      "end": 1124.74,
      "text": "He was helping her"
    },
    {
      "start": 1124.84,
      "end": 1125.66,
      "text": "and they killed him,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1125.78,
      "end": 1126.9,
      "text": "and now she's..."
    },
    {
      "start": 1127.06,
      "end": 1127.72,
      "text": "Oh,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1127.8,
      "end": 1128.6,
      "text": "you've got to go,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1128.72,
      "end": 1129.0,
      "text": "Sam!"
    },
    {
      "start": 1130.08,
      "end": 1130.46,
      "text": "All right.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1131.84,
      "end": 1134.18,
      "text": "Spade pushed her away and bent over his desk,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1134.3,
      "end": 1135.02,
      "text": "putting the"
    },
    {
      "start": 1135.06,
      "end": 1137.28,
      "text": "blackbird back into its nest of Excelsior,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1137.44,
      "end": 1138.8,
      "text": "bending the paper around"
    },
    {
      "start": 1139.02,
      "end": 1139.14,
      "text": "it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1139.18,
      "end": 1140.02,
      "text": "working swiftly,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1140.32,
      "end": 1142.64,
      "text": "making a larger and clumsy package."
    },
    {
      "start": 1143.79,
      "end": 1145.12,
      "text": "As soon as I've gone,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1145.26,
      "end": 1145.96,
      "text": "phone the police."
    },
    {
      "start": 1146.72,
      "end": 1147.64,
      "text": "Tell them how it happened,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1147.8,
      "end": 1149.28,
      "text": "but don't drag any names"
    },
    {
      "start": 1149.28,
      "end": 1149.46,
      "text": "in."
    },
    {
      "start": 1149.66,
      "end": 1150.76,
      "text": "You don't know."
    },
    {
      "start": 1151.84,
      "end": 1152.82,
      "text": "I got the phone call,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1152.98,
      "end": 1154.7,
      "text": "and I told you I had to go out,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1154.82,
      "end": 1155.54,
      "text": "but I didn't"
    },
    {
      "start": 1155.54,
      "end": 1155.98,
      "text": "say where."
    },
    {
      "start": 1157.42,
      "end": 1159.18,
      "text": "He cursed the rope for being tangled,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1159.44,
      "end": 1160.8,
      "text": "yanked it into straightness,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1160.96,
      "end": 1161.52,
      "text": "and began to"
    },
    {
      "start": 1161.58,
      "end": 1162.4,
      "text": "bind up the package."
    },
    {
      "start": 1163.904,
      "end": 1164.6,
      "text": "Forget this thing.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1165.36,
      "end": 1166.23,
      "text": "Tell it as it happened,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1166.4,
      "end": 1167.7,
      "text": "but forget he had a bundle."
    },
    {
      "start": 1168.5,
      "end": 1170.3,
      "text": "He chewed his lower lip.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1171.232,
      "end": 1172.46,
      "text": "\"'Unless they pin you down.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1173.1,
      "end": 1174.42,
      "text": "If they seem to know about it,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1174.48,
      "end": 1175.58,
      "text": "you'll have to admit it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1176.4,
      "end": 1177.26,
      "text": "But that's not likely.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1178.14,
      "end": 1178.56,
      "text": "If they do,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1178.76,
      "end": 1181.23,
      "text": "then I took the bundle away with me unopened.'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1182.13,
      "end": 1184.62,
      "text": "He finished tying the knot and straightened",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1184.62,
      "end": 1186.42,
      "text": "up with the parcel under his left arm."
    },
    {
      "start": 1187.52,
      "end": 1188.3,
      "text": "\"'Get it straight now.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1188.928,
      "end": 1190.5,
      "text": "Everything happened the way it happened,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1190.92,
      "end": 1193.3,
      "text": "but without this dingus unless they already know"
    },
    {
      "start": 1193.3,
      "end": 1193.8,
      "text": "about it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1194.56,
      "end": 1195.22,
      "text": "Don't deny it,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1195.34,
      "end": 1196.38,
      "text": "just don't mention it."
    },
    {
      "start": 1196.52,
      "end": 1198.3,
      "text": "And I got the phone call,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1198.42,
      "end": 1199.08,
      "text": "not you."
    },
    {
      "start": 1200.0,
      "end": 1202.72,
      "text": "And you don't know anything about anybody else having any",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1202.84,
      "end": 1203.8,
      "text": "connection with this fellow."
    },
    {
      "start": 1204.64,
      "end": 1206.02,
      "text": "You don't know anything about him,",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1206.06,
      "end": 1207.12,
      "text": "and you can't talk about"
    },
    {
      "start": 1207.12,
      "end": 1208.6,
      "text": "my business until you see me."
    },
    {
      "start": 1209.34,
      "end": 1209.76,
      "text": "Got it?\"",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1210.3,
      "end": 1210.98,
      "text": "\"'Yes,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1210.98,
      "end": 1211.28,
      "text": "Sam."
    },
    {
      "start": 1212.064,
      "end": 1213.76,
      "text": "Who—do you know who he is?'"
    },
    {
      "start": 1214.74,
      "end": 1215.96,
      "text": "He grinned wolfishly.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1216.98,
      "end": 1218.02,
      "text": "\"'Uh-uh,' he said.",
      "para_break": true
    },
    {
      "start": 1218.66,
      "end": 1220.48,
      "text": "But I'd guess he was Captain Jacoby,"
    },
    {
      "start": 1220.7,
      "end": 1222.26,
      "text": "late master of the Paloma.\""
    },
    {
      "start": 1222.91,
      "end": 1224.94,
      "text": "He picked up his hat and put it on."
    },
    {
      "start": 1225.32,
      "end": 1228.32,
      "text": "He looked thoughtfully at the dead man and then around the room."
    }
  ]
}